{"tid":381854,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【世界議事會小說】ＣＨ１：世……議事……會誠……加入……議員","createTime":"2017-08-31T09:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T09:14:52.000Z","uid":46784,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76dd5fd8272c095b75af091632315e2ac6895c19","tid":381854,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:34:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/173430_4339d9fe6e491018052c2eb01ba5b397.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F173430_4339d9fe6e491018052c2eb01ba5b397.jpg&h=49513238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日成日話南北韓局勢緊張，肥仔恩準備射核彈。但我喺香港，驚都未驚過啦！<br />\n　<br />\n打起仗黎，最多咪金價大升、股市大跌，我又未到擔心呢啲嘢嘅時候喎。<br />\n　<br />\n啱啱畢業出嚟打份工，星期五有得早放都多謝老細啦。<br />\n　<br />\n咁啱我係做facebook page嘅記者，平日專門寫埋啲戇鳩嘢，氹下大家開心：嘩，抹茶紫薯，好邪惡呀！（好多Like啊！）<br />\n　<br />\n其實我讀傳理系，本身係諗住做過好記者架，出到嚟揭發下社會嘅不公不義，最好就搵個好似batman咁嘅超級英雄同我合作下啦&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n　<br />\n當然啦，係嗰陣十幾歲人睇得太多marvel電影&hellip;&hellip;（Sor，之後先發現batman唔係marvel，不過算啦，有咩香港人記得啫。）<br />\n　<br />\n話說嗰日星期五照常六點放，出到門口個天紅紅地，日落餘輝映照喺幾道飛機噴射雲上面，係難得一見嘅清澈晴空&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n　<br />\n而我，係混濁嘅城市人流入面，湧向地鐵站&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n　<br />\n我耳邊係紅綠燈有節奏嘅聲，同埋人潮嘅粗口，同埋飛機劃過天際嘅聲音。<br />\n　<br />\n之後第二聲、第三聲&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n　<br />\n我心入面覺得奇怪之後抬頭一望。有幾架好似飛機咁嘅嘢喺天空向唔同方向飛過，但係點解架飛機咁奇怪，冇機翼嘅？<br />\n　<br />\n似乎有唔少人都不約而同咁望向天空，發現到呢個異象。<br />\n　<br />\n最奇怪嘅係，其中一架冇翼飛機好似墜落咁高速向遙遠嘅港島俯衝落去。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook Page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/csTheWorldCouncil/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FcsTheWorldCouncil%2F&d=WDMGX52A1KcV%2Fr3RIxTRRv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=0c3651ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/csTheWorldCouncil/</a>"},{"pid":"489ee9f0f28911f221bedacb676963e1923a4a8f","tid":381854,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:35:44.000Z","msg":"好多人仲喺度哇、哇、哇，但我忽然覺得唔係好對路。<br />\n　<br />\n心入面嘅恐懼迫使我衝向靜止嘅人流，向地鐵站深處跑去<br />\n　<br />\n「借借！唔好意思、借借！」<br />\n　<br />\n身邊嘅周圍忽然比光芒充滿咗&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n　<br />\n唔係太陽光咁簡單，係好光好光，忽然所有嘢都幾乎變為白色。<br />\n　<br />\n眼前只有好模糊嘅人影，然後我聽到吱一聲，全世界都好似淨咗落嚟。<br />\n　<br />\n我聽唔到任何聲音，好多人跌低咗，好多人開始向前推&hellip;&hellip;到底發生咩事？<br />\n　<br />\n我咩都聽唔到，點解我咩聲都聽唔到嘅？<br />\n　<br />\n我開始跌跌撞撞咁跟住人群跑落地鐵站，伴隨住耳鳴，我覺得好痛苦，隻耳仔好似有啲野留緊出嚟咁&hellip;&hellip;係血？<br />\n　<br />\n血？<br />\n　<br />\n我心跳不斷咁加速，即使身體不斷咁被人碰撞，我依然繼續向前跑。<br />\n　<br />\n與其話我係自己跑，不如話我係比人推住跑。我見到好多人跌低咗，畀後面嘅人踩咗落地下，人浪就好似真嘅浪一樣，一波一波向前湧&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n　<br />\n我好似慢慢咁恢復聽覺，見到好多人八達通都唔拍，直接跳入去閘入面。<br />\n　<br />\n我第一件聽到嘅聲音係自己部電話響。"},{"pid":"c6f44a189dd189186cc321fb3cf18179c4533b7e","tid":381854,"uid":46784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:36:27.000Z","msg":"到底我係咪真係聽到？其實定係我只係feel到佢震機？<br />\n　<br />\n唔理啦&hellip;&hellip;我拎起部電話一望，見到係未有來電顯示&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n　<br />\n唔通係老闆叫我返公司執埋手尾？<br />\n　<br />\n梗係唔係啦，我講下笑㗎咋。<br />\n　<br />\n我嗰下竟然有心情停低接呢個電話。<br />\n　<br />\n「喂？喂？」<br />\n　<br />\n「&hellip;&hellip;世&hellip;&hellip;議事&hellip;&hellip;會誠&hellip;&hellip;加入&hellip;&hellip;議員&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n　<br />\n「&hellip;&hellip;喂？」<br />\n　<br />\n「議員&hellip;&hellip;編號：01852&hellip;&hellip;正在定位&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n　<br />\n「喂？ 你唔好玩我啦，我聽唔到你講嘢呀&hellip;&hellip;」訊號收得好差，我嘅聽覺亦都好差。我只係好隱約聽到佢講緊啲乜。<br />\n　<br />\n我抬頭，見到兩個著住黑色西裝戴黑超嘅人畢直咁向我行過嚟&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n　<br />\n？？？！？<br />\n　<br />\n我諗住逃走，但係人流不斷將我推向黑衣人嘅方向！<br />\n　<br />\n黐線㗎！到底香港發生咩事？點解我會遇上呢啲咁嘅奇怪嘢架？<br />\n　<br />\n我忽然察覺到頸上面好似蚊針咁痛咗一下，之後我覺得眼皮越來越重&hellip;&hellip;慢慢咁失去咗知覺&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n　<br />\n「Take him to the chopper! Now!」<br />\n　<br />\n「&hellip;&hellip;Tactical strike area, central. Estimated casualties, 210000.」<br />\n<br />\n（待續）"},{"pid":"c88d9f4b65bc8fcd9370830f23e35812562745d6","tid":381854,"uid":107206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:42:21.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4b1391a3c8980622cc93d68eff5964eb82891113","tid":381854,"uid":23323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:49:21.000Z","msg":"正呀喂<br />\n留名出多幾章"},{"pid":"442da85c4cfcd021c603d78ea9781134fa9616a1","tid":381854,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:51:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正呀喂<br />\n留名出多幾章</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比個正皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7ecd9a86aeb752f59fb41c5d8d1ece42b22e1c","tid":381854,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:34:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f9b96148a76248704946f75ebb96d60f0abe3f79","tid":381854,"uid":10978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:38:05.000Z","msg":"皮已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5611e4f6def010ffcec27c01ea11062cee6eced9","tid":381854,"uid":22259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"得兩篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63b1004638c1a868bc3e15e5479937203fab76b","tid":381854,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:30:01.000Z","msg":"嘩<br />\n咁撚少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7d09ec84d9d3a0b68148b6933fd3e68e72ca8b","tid":381854,"uid":141554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:44:50.000Z","msg":"正皮已比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd61f4e8a4dc2bc41c4cd2c51ea29b86cbe59fc","tid":381854,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:53:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c2d53f620bcf99eb886b9ca6a16c6574d739ba89","tid":381854,"uid":108606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T18:29:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ae7d517808f41eb18bb8887c854e2cc6ebf2f3fc","tid":381854,"uid":141554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:14:52.000Z","msg":"文呢？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}